{"tid":1158840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾說 【我的六四故事】我是記者馮偉光 - 香港大遊行聲援北京民運","createTime":"2019-05-17T08:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T09:27:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"319b4fab95c53886d73393958e1efd66e51d0f5a","tid":1158840,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/20581/我是記者・我的六四故事-六四30年-馮偉光-20581/【我的六四故事】我是記者馮偉光-香港大遊行聲援北京民運\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F20581%2F%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E3%83%BB%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B30%E5%B9%B4-%E9%A6%AE%E5%81%89%E5%85%89-20581%2F%E3%80%90%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%91%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%A6%AE%E5%81%89%E5%85%89-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%81%8B&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=e2850e96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/20581/我是記者・我的六四故事-六四30年-馮偉光-20581/【我的六四故事】我是記者馮偉光-香港大遊行聲援北京民運</a><br />\n<br />\n眾說<br />\n【我的六四故事】我是記者馮偉光 - 香港大遊行聲援北京民運<br />\n<br />\n撰文: 我是記者・我的六四故事 | 發佈日期: 17.05.19<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請支持《眾新聞》，成為訂戶<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jaB8sXe0FJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjaB8sXe0FJs&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=287a0b8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jaB8sXe0FJs</a><br />\n<br />\n馮偉光筆名盧峯，1989年任職百姓半月刊記者，在港採訪聲援北京民運的大遊行，目睹港人正義感，及對中國改革的期望。30年後有些年青人抵制悼念六四，他由譴責漸變為理解。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/facebook-64-follow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ffacebook-64-follow&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=e571c86d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/facebook-64-follow</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/youtube-64-subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fyoutube-64-subscribe&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=43d526cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/youtube-64-subscribe</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請加入成為眾新聞的月費訂戶，長期支持我們的工作。所有訂戶都可以收到我們的「每周時事」通訊 。<br />\n<br />\n月費訂戶網址：<a href=\"http://hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Faboutus%2F%23subscribe&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=0bb77337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe</a><br />\n<br />\n博客 | 我是記者・我的六四故事<br />\n2019 年是「六四」30 周年。30 年過去，不僅參與者暴亂惡名未洗刷、死難者沉冤未昭雪，更兼且當年事態日漸備受歪曲、或年輕人已無從瞭解事件經過。因此，當年曾身歷其境的記者，有責任將當日所見所聞、日後所思所感，再做一次紀錄，公諸於世，以為歷史見證。2018 年底，一批記者行家醞釀了這個再做紀錄的項目，得到香港記者協會的支持，並申請《人民不會忘記》基金資助，分別以文字和影像來做記述。"},{"pid":"98c11681b6d1f2874d9f317a20494bc9dbe99f85","tid":1158840,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bd0fd444d0ee68addcbab40cf8865847c367bc","tid":1158840,"uid":185606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"以為係嗰件垃圾馮煒光"}]}